source.name: Business Enterprise Architecture Terms and Definitions (AV-2)
source.description: The AV-2 (annotated for DM2) release 6.0 includes all the terms and definitions in the BEA and where appropriate, the term tagged with the DoDAF MetaModel concepts for Capability, Activity, Resources and Performers.
